:.START

From Sept. 30oct. 4 Economist Issue

Aoun wey win di war, no be only wetin Siria sojas lose.

Di tins wey happen to Lebanon pipol, na di same tin with wetin happen to Israel pipol before.

But Israel pipol dey trit dem like sey dem bi Lebanon enemy.

Di best hope wey im neighbour get for us, na when we settle quarrel with di Palestinians.

Israel pipol bi like Mount Lebanon wey dey produce picture.

Greater Israel pipol get pass half of di shidren wey dey under six.

E no go reach like 25 years before Jew people go dey minority.

But Israel no go get pawa with all dis Arab people and na wetin dia king talk, na im e go do. E go draw evriwhere near Jerusalem till di year wey dem born am.

If Israel pipol no choose any of dis option, dem go condemn demsef, like Maron pipol, dem go fight demsef with Muslim pipol wey dey dia side, and na dis go cause wahala for dia state.

Israel pipol nor go bi like Maron pipol wey go weak pass oda pipol. Dem go bi like Belfast before e go rish Lebanon.

But dat one no be sey di General Aoun no do well.

